msgid "1. 简介"
msgstr "1. Introduction"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:7
#: 2cfda2e8bf9243e89f52dd6ab36dbc1b
msgid ""
"安信可科技针对物联网设计通用型的蓝牙模组，其功能强大、用途广泛。可以用于智能"
"灯、智能插座、智能空调等其他智能家电。同时符合BLE 5.0及SIG Mesh规范，可直接通"
"过智能手机组建Mesh网络，也可对接天猫精灵智能音箱，适用于多种智能家居应用场"
"景。"
msgstr ""
"Ai-Thinker Technology has designed a general-purpose Bluetooth module for "
"IoT applications. It is powerful and widely applicable, and can be used in "
"smart lights, smart sockets, smart air conditioners, and other smart home "
"appliances. It also complies with BLE 5.0 and SIG Mesh specifications. A "
"Mesh network can be created directly via a smartphone, and it can also be "
"connected to Tmall Genie smart speakers, making it suitable for various "
"smart home application scenarios."

