"appears in the device list.  **Only two commands are needed.** ::"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:111
#: a1049568910840d0960e13c1064dedf7
msgid "3.2 权限问题 /dev/ttyUSB0"
msgstr "3.2 Permission Issue: /dev/ttyUSB0"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:112
#: 4ccf3013a31243bfbc756e4da27bde72
msgid ""
"**使用某些 Linux 版本向 TB-02 烧写固件时，可能会出现 Failed to open port /"
"dev/ttyUSB0 错误消息。此时，可以将当前用户增加至 :ref: `Linux Dialout 组 "
"<linux-dialout-group>`。**"
msgstr ""
"**When flashing firmware to the TB-02 using some Linux versions, the error "
"message \"Failed to open port /dev/ttyUSB0\" may appear. In this case, you "
"can add the current user to the: `Linux Dialout Group <linux-dialout-group>`."
"**"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:114
#: 667f41a1fe5d4053a9f72f0befe8a0a1
msgid ""
"因为默认情况下，只有root用户和属于dialout组的用户会有读写权限，因此直接把自己"
"的用户加入到dialout组就可以了。操作完命令后要重启一下，就永久生效了。 ::"
msgstr ""
"By default, only the root user and users belonging to the dialout group have "
"read and write permissions. Therefore, you can simply add your user account "
"to the dialout group. After running the command, restart the system, and the "
"change will take effect permanently. ::"
